{"tid":1455311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨圍長春同依家圍機場一樣 機場依家唔走真係走唔到，快啲走","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:14:52.000Z","uid":77164,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"09a29d55a5423c97d1fad4139474673ae400a25f","tid":1455311,"uid":77164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"香港機場唔係廿四個鐘都有飛機飛，你唔走就要留到聽日四五點先得，依家舖頭閂哂即係無野食無水飲，遲啲冷氣燈都閂埋你點算？快啲走啦<br />\n<br />\n依家停飛機，下一步就係停巴士，停機場快線。就算你想幫手有幾多架私家車入到去？班警犬會俾你入咩？<br />\n<br />\n佢肯停哂啲機已經好有問題！停半日就可以停一日停兩日。就算聽日會照開返，義士可以頂幾耐？無水無糧留十二個鐘俾警犬圍，佢地搞唔掂你地？人多咪拉外圍先囉，八個一定搞得掂<br />\n<br />\n走啦咁多位"},{"pid":"4f436553079b0c4726934ea0781a9df20568a9a8","tid":1455311,"uid":77164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:53:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8efb22cf6b9ea3a6cac72bf9ce6385ef83a6a72e","tid":1455311,"uid":77164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"大家都想香港好，唔好分鬼，自己思考"},{"pid":"e72c1649f740b4e8b7b2a42a9f5d4696a976ab02","tid":1455311,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:58:16.000Z","msg":"建議走<br />\n不過機場係廿四小時"},{"pid":"296ae2c78e8886fa624c4190aca1b9329e4f70a6","tid":1455311,"uid":77164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:58:50.000Z","msg":"重點重點！聽住。前地勤教路，如果有需要請打火警鐘，機場設計火警鐘一響，所有門都會開哂"},{"pid":"d383b835477afc140fb80425c8df9a677b8db280","tid":1455311,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ebf8469b1e2bf40446b5ccf9edeaa3a720ce38","tid":1455311,"uid":77164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e72c1649f740b4e8b7b2a42a9f5d4696a976ab02","tid":1455311,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:58:16.000Z","msg":"建議走<br />\n不過機場係廿四小時"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi